benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: PUT /1.0/kb/bundles/{bundleId}/customFields - Modify custom fields to bundle

covered: Valid Request: Scenarios cover successful modification of custom fields with valid payloads.
Invalid Payload: Multiple scenarios test for various invalid payloads and headers.
Non-Existing Resource: Scenarios handle attempts to modify non-existent bundles.
Partial Update: Scenarios address partial updates and variations in custom fields.
gaps: Concurrency Issues: No tests cover race conditions when multiple users try to update the same resource.
Rate Limiting: No tests cover how the system handles multiple requests in a short time.
recommendations: Add tests for concurrency issues to ensure data integrity during simultaneous updates.
Include rate limiting tests to verify system behavior under high request loads.
